well my life is goin pretty good. last night sucked, we lost to bayside :( . i should be at flager whoopin butt, but my parents didnt want me to miss school, i understand where they are comin from though. my new math class is cake, thats a load off my back. right now im just hanging aorund waitin for tony pajamas. i have linkin park blaring woot woot!!! tomorrow its movie night at calieghs, then sunday........idk another night at the beach? we will just have to wait and see. Ap gov is a cool class, it can get, well the reading can get monotonous.......yeah big word, go me :-P . yeah i almost got in a fight today after i got off the bus, some teens are dumb, he tried startin stuff with kyle, and then he thought he was going to get physical with one of my friends, ill give the kid credit though, he walked away, i dont know if he realized it was pointless to attempt to fight, or if wised up for real. i hope he realized that fighting just digs a hole for you, idk . dammit anthony get here.........im writing this and adding to it over like a 45 minute time period. ahahhaha. there is so much im looking forward to though, wrestling, mixed martial arts in a few months, laurens dance comp, mock trial comp, i cant wait woot woot~~~~~~~~!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

well i dont know when the last time i updated this is sooooooo yeah. here goesssssss. the past few days have been great, some rough patches here and there, but nothing major, its been goin well. this past weekend, was just flat out incredible, and Sunday night was just unbelieveable.Schools been going well, and i did well on my report card, parents are happy and i go back to wrestling. i love that sport, but it doesnt come without its sacrifices, all my friends need to understand that, and i think they do. the rest of the week is way up in the air, Wednesday evening im hanging out with lauren, but i may end up missing school friday for Flager wrestling tourney, thursday night is away at bayside, i have to talk to coach about the whole room on the bus deal, so i will find about all that tomorrow. well im going to leave some favorite little blurbs of songs or what not for you so i will ttyl!

On a dark desert highway, cool wind in my hair
Warm smell of colitas, rising up through the air
Up ahead in the distance, I saw a shimmering light
My head grew heavy and my sight grew dim
I had to stop for the night
There she stood in the doorway;
I heard the mission bell
And I was thinking to myself,
'This could be Heaven or this could be Hell'
Then she lit up a candle and she showed me the way
There were voices down the corridor,
I thought I heard them say...

Welcome to the Hotel California
Such a lovely place
Such a lovely face
Plenty of room at the Hotel California
Any time of year, you can find it here

Her mind is Tiffany-twisted, she got the Mercedes bends
She got a lot of pretty, pretty boys, that she calls friends
How they dance in the courtyard, sweet summer sweat.
Some dance to remember, some dance to forget

So I called up the Captain,
'Please bring me my wine'
He said, 'We haven't had that spirit here since nineteen sixty nine'
And still those voices are calling from far away,
Wake you up in the middle of the night
Just to hear them say...

Welcome to the Hotel California
Such a lovely place
Such a lovely face
They livin' it up at the Hotel California
What a nice surprise, bring your alibis

Mirrors on the ceiling,
The pink champagne on ice
And she said 'We are all just prisoners here, of our own device'
And in the master's chambers,
They gathered for the feast
The stab it with their steely knives,
But they just can't kill the beast

Last thing I remember, I was
Running for the door
I had to find the passage back
To the place I was before
'Relax,' said the night man,
We are programmed to receive.
You can checkout any time you like,
but you can never leave!

well after i woke up today i just hung around all day,it was kind of my chill out day, sometime when you see people too much you can get ground down, so it was nice to have some on-my-own-time. i didnt really tlak to anyone at all i just the away message up and just lazed around. The whole church deal, i have decided that i dont need a church to help me become a better person, i believe in God, but Churches are just to overbearing and right now the last thing i want is an entity telling me how to live my life or how evil or w/e i am. i want to keep my mind open, churches dont allow that. i dont think i will be attending Advent Lutheran anymore. for new years i will have family here, Christian might come over, but AJ cant make it...so idk i may invite someone else. but one question who will i kiss on new years? hahah JK! im really hoping that my parents will let me go back to wrestling, training wise right now im fat cutting, i put on muscle now im just trimming the fat off, what little of it i have. so yeah. after wrestling is over im going to do okinawan kenpo, i think that will help me with my mixed martial arts because my stand-up game sucks terribly. for those of you that dont have a clue what im talking about, when i compete/fight in mixed martial art im not good at standing and punching kicking etc. im good at taking them down and submitting them (choking, armbars etc) i mean i haveskills but i wouldnt stand with anyone. i havent fought in like 3 years, goin to a dojo will help immensly. well im outta here.
